  <num>28:1-106</num>
  <heading>Use of singular and plural; gender.</heading>
  <text>In this subtitle, unless the statutory context otherwise requires:</text>
  <level>
    <num>(1)</num>
    <text>Words in the singular number include the plural, and those in the plural include the singular; and</text>
  </level>
  <level>
    <num>(2)</num>
    <text>Words of any gender also refer to any other gender.</text>
  </level>
